房子是我哥哥巴塞洛缪的
The house belongs to my brother, Bartholomew.

235
00:21:56,674 --> 00:21:58,811
我选择离开
I chose to leave.

236
00:21:59,813 --> 00:22:01,178
她怀孕了
She's with child.

237
